Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.27,0:00:07.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...is quite common in school life dramas...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.60,0:00:11.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and I'd be lying if I said I'd never dreamed about such an experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.26,0:00:15.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And now I am presently living out my dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.99,0:00:19.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wonder why I'm not the least bit happy about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.45,0:00:20.67,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That way, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.67,0:00:22.10,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.10,0:00:23.65,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.66,0:00:32.17,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're getting close to Nagato's apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.05,0:02:07.00,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like Asakura lived in room 505 in this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.78,0:02:09.79,HaruhiTitleOverlay,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\fs28\fad(490,460)\pos(626,44)}The Melancholy of Haruhi Suzumiya V
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.47,0:02:08.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.60,0:02:10.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,See what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.15,0:02:11.46,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.85,0:02:14.04,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, how are you planning on getting inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.66,0:02:16.46,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know the code for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.75,0:02:17.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.71,0:02:19.56,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a battle of attrition.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.52,0:02:29.02,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.17,0:02:33.03,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Get in here already!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.32,0:02:35.58,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, it's definitely strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.58,0:02:37.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She suddenly transferred to Canada...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.23,0:02:39.81,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...and no one knows her new address.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.81,0:02:41.33,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You already told me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.33,0:02:43.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And that isn't the only thing that's fishy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:47.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't seem to have attended any of the local middle schools either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.71,0:02:49.36,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.36,0:02:53.73,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I did some snooping and found out she transferred from a school in the suburbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.73,0:02:55.20,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that suspicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.20,0:02:58.03,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,North High isn't famous or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.03,0:03:00.03,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just your typical prefectural high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.03,0:03:02.21,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would she go out of her way to attend here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.21,0:03:02.98,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.98,0:03:05.79,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet her residence is this close to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.79,0:03:07.19,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's a condo at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.19,0:03:09.42,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a rental apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.42,0:03:11.74,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,In a nice location like this it must be insanely expensive!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.74,0:03:14.03,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Has she been commuting to her middle school in the suburbs from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.03,0:03:14.98,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, I dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.23,0:03:18.91,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we'll need to find out when Asakura began living here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.16,0:03:20.63,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's empty now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.63,0:03:21.83,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The door won't open.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.58,0:03:25.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm thinking this is a waste of time, even for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.38,0:03:28.13,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to the manager's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.13,0:03:30.65,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt he'll let you borrow a key.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.65,0:03:31.85,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.85,0:03:34.41,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to ask him when Asakura began living here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.41,0:03:36.10,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just give up and go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.10,0:03:38.26,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What can you possibly accomplish with that information?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.26,0:03:38.93,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.39,0:03:43.35,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We're friends of a former resident, Ryoko Asakura-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.90,0:03:45.93,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She suddenly moved...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.93,0:03:48.35,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...and we don't know how to contact her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.59,0:03:50.96,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you happen to hear where she moved to?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.96,0:03:54.98,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And I was wondering if you could tell me when Asakura-san came to this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.98,0:03:57.57,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So she can phrase questions like a normal human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.65,0:04:02.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering if you could tell me where...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.99,0:04:04.63,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...Ryoko Asakura-san moved...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.63,0:04:05.69,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...or when she began living here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.53,0:04:10.30,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Asakura-san in room 505, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.30,0:04:14.26,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I was shocked when I found the room empty...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.26,0:04:16.13,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...when I hadn't seen any movers come by.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.13,0:04:17.37,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Must have slipped past me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:19.79,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No movers came...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.79,0:04:22.21,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't hear where she moved either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.21,0:04:25.75,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If they get a package later on, I won't know where to send it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.75,0:04:27.31,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite troubling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.68,0:04:29.81,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When did she begin living here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.21,0:04:32.68,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Three years ago, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.13,0:04:38.55,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember since the lovely young lady brought me a box of confections.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.55,0:04:39.98,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What about her parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.98,0:04:43.43,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what line of work her father and mother were in?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:45.13,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.13,0:04:45.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.89,0:04:48.72,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw the young lady a number of times...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.72,0:04:51.67,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I don't recall ever meeting her parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.09,0:04:54.46,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is an expensive apartment, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.46,0:04:58.92,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see them taking out a loan on a place just for their child.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.28,0:05:00.59,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.59,0:05:01.78,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No loan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.78,0:05:04.37,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She paid a lump sum up front in cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.37,0:05:06.78,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose she was filthy rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.81,0:05:07.55,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}Impressive interrogating.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.55,0:05:08.73,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}You should become a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.13,0:05:12.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She could have at least said goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.24,0:05:13.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.99,0:05:15.29,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.29,0:05:18.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...you're a fine-looking girl yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.33,0:05:22.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.12,0:05:26.61,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Lad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.71,0:05:30.88,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That young lady will definitely grow up to be a beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.88,0:05:32.70,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let her get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.96,0:05:38.82,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.83,0:05:43.80,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Guess she actually eats food.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.13,0:05:46.50,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you live here too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.50,0:05:47.00,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.45,0:05:49.22,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's obviously not a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.49,0:05:52.36,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then did you hear anything about Asakura?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.36,0:05:54.07,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You know that she transferred, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.36,0:05:56.16,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.16,0:05:58.35,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If you learn anything about Asakura, let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.35,0:05:59.17,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.11,0:06:01.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to your glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.36,0:06:05.32,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're making me uncomfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.75,0:06:12.50,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.65,0:06:18.16,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Be careful of what this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.81,0:06:19.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.23,0:06:31.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we going now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:32.31,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.80,0:06:33.77,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.57,0:06:42.03,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I go home now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.16,0:06:50.37,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.37,0:06:55.04,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever realized how insignificant your existence is on this planet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.04,0:06:56.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.44,0:06:58.46,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.96,0:07:00.63,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's something I'll never forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.63,0:07:02.11,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,During elementary school...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.11,0:07:03.53,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was in sixth grade...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.53,0:07:06.26,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...the whole family went to watch a baseball game...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.26,0:07:07.30,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...at the stadium.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.75,0:07:10.43,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't particularly interested in baseball...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.43,0:07:11.64,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I was shocked once we got there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.32,0:07:14.79,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There were people everywhere I looked.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.79,0:07:19.05,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The ones on the other side of the stadium looked like squirming grains of rice all packed together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.69,0:07:23.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I wondered if every last person in Japan had gathered in this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.71,0:07:24.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.48,0:07:26.36,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...I asked my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.36,0:07:29.21,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly how many people were in the stadium?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.59,0:07:32.68,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,His answer was that a sold-out game meant around fifty thousand people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.01,0:07:36.53,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,After the game, the path to the station was flooded with people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.53,0:07:39.13,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The sight stunned me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.13,0:07:41.56,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So many people around me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.56,0:07:46.14,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...yet they only made up a fraction of the people in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.14,0:07:48.77,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I got home, I got a calculator and did the math.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.77,0:07:53.08,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We learned that the Japanese population was a hundred million and some in social studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.08,0:07:55.22,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Divide fifty thousand into that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.02,0:07:57.87,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...and you only get one two-thousandth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.17,0:08:00.04,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I was stunned again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.36,0:08:04.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only was I just one little person in that sea of people in that stadium...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.89,0:08:07.45,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...but that sea of people...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.45,0:08:10.03,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...was merely a drop in the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.86,0:08:12.47,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I had thought myself to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.47,0:08:15.78,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...a special person up until that point.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.78,0:08:17.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I enjoyed being with my family...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.99,0:08:19.01,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...and most of all...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.01,0:08:21.36,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...I thought that my class in my school...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.36,0:08:24.80,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...had the most interesting people in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.28,0:08:26.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.15,0:08:28.57,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...that was when I realized it wasn't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.29,0:08:33.19,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The things that happened in what I believed to be the most enjoyable class in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.19,0:08:37.05,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...could be found happening in any school in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.76,0:08:41.96,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone in Japan would find them to be ordinary occurrences.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.46,0:08:44.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I realized this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.23,0:08:45.86,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...I suddenly found that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.86,0:08:49.27,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...my surroundings were beginning to lose their color.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.54,0:08:52.62,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Brush my teeth and go to sleep at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.62,0:08:54.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up and eat breakfast in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.99,0:08:56.36,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,People do those everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.36,0:08:59.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When I realized that everyone did all these things on a daily basis...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.66,0:09:01.96,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...everything started to feel so boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.56,0:09:03.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And if...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.51,0:09:05.68,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...there were so many people in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.68,0:09:09.68,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...there had to be someone living an interesting life that wasn't ordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.68,0:09:11.81,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I was sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.53,0:09:14.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why wasn't that person me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.47,0:09:17.53,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all I could think about...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.53,0:09:19.94,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...until I graduated from elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.50,0:09:22.38,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And in the process, I realized something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.70,0:09:25.85,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing fun will happen if you sit around waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.24,0:09:29.78,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So I figured I would change myself in middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.78,0:09:33.41,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let the world know that I wasn't a girl content with sitting around and waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.41,0:09:35.40,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And I conducted myself accordingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.90,0:09:37.86,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But in the end, nothing ever happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.20,0:09:41.28,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Before I knew it, I was in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.98,0:09:44.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought something would have changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.87,0:09:56.70,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The train gave me time...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.70,0:09:58.50,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...to decide if I should make a witty comment...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.50,0:10:01.61,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...or quote some philosophical anecdote...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.61,0:10:03.01,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...to fill up the silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.34,0:10:04.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.49,0:10:07.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My inability to say anything else...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.71,0:10:09.20,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...made me a bit melancholic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.20,0:10:10.02,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.74,0:10:17.10,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.10,0:10:19.96,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...it would be faster to go home that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.96,0:10:21.94,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...but I got the feeling that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.94,0:10:25.47,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...Haruhi's back was silently yelling, "Don't follow me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.47,0:10:29.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So until Haruhi was out of sight...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.25,0:10:31.13,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...I just stood there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.70,0:10:33.64,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.03,0:10:40.11,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.59,0:10:44.76,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to fulfill my prior promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.29,0:10:47.40,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for your return.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.71,0:10:49.63,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You sound like...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.63,0:10:51.44,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...you know where I went.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.87,0:10:55.10,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Could I have a bit of your time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.08,0:10:58.33,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzumiya-related?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.80,0:11:00.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzumiya-san-related.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.47,0:11:06.50,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This taxi sure passed by at a perfect time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.01,0:11:07.88,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.21,0:11:11.84,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanted proof that I was an esper, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.61,0:11:14.95,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,An opportunity has arrived...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.95,0:11:16.90,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I thought you might want to come along.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.31,0:11:19.39,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a point in traveling so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.91,0:11:23.63,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I can only demonstrate my powers as an esper...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.63,0:11:25.06,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...in a certain location...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.06,0:11:27.00,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...under certain conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.44,0:11:29.47,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Our current destination...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.47,0:11:32.40,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...happens to fulfill those conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.80,0:11:35.19,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you still think Haruhi is God or whatever?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.70,0:11:38.88,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you aware of the anthropic principle?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.88,0:11:40.67,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Never heard of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.67,0:11:42.54,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The condensed version is as follows.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.54,0:11:45.02,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,''If something must be true for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.02,0:11:47.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...as humans, to exist...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.25,0:11:49.74,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...then it is true because we exist."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.05,0:11:50.92,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.21,0:11:52.30,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No idea what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.06,0:11:54.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I observe...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.51,0:11:56.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...therefore the universe exists...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.49,0:11:57.96,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...would be another way to put it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.33,0:11:59.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.48,0:12:02.72,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...humans, the intelligent life forms of this planet...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.72,0:12:05.30,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...discovered the laws of physics and other physical constants...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.30,0:12:09.31,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...and through those discoveries, became aware for the first time...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.31,0:12:11.98,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...of the existence of a universe bound by those observations.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.43,0:12:15.34,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, if the humans on Earth who observed this universe...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.34,0:12:18.46,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...had not evolved to our current level...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.46,0:12:20.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...there would be no one to make those observations...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.48,0:12:23.45,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...and consequently, the existence of the universe would remain unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.45,0:12:26.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, it wouldn't matter if the universe existed or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.71,0:12:30.77,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The existence of humans permits the existence of the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.77,0:12:32.42,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This would be the reasoning from a human basis.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.68,0:12:34.68,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.68,0:12:36.14,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't matter if humans are around or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.14,0:12:36.92,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The universe is the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.42,0:12:38.53,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.53,0:12:42.50,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is why the anthropic principle is merely speculative theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.50,0:12:45.47,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,However, it brings some interesting facts to our attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.64,0:12:48.31,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did the universe happen to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.31,0:12:51.56,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...created to accommodate human life?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.56,0:12:52.81,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If there was a slight increase or decrease...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.81,0:12:54.45,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...in the gravitational constant...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.45,0:12:56.13,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...or particle-mass ratios...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.13,0:12:59.14,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...the universe would most likely not have facilitated the development of such a planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.14,0:13:00.86,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You sound like one of those brochures...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.86,0:13:03.69,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...for one of those new pseudoscience religions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.14,0:13:05.46,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Quite frankly...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.46,0:13:07.61,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...I do not believe that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.61,0:13:09.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...an omniscient, omnipotent God...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.51,0:13:11.81,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...created humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.81,0:13:13.58,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,However, we have our suspicions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.58,0:13:14.80,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.80,0:13:17.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps we are just clowns standing on tiptoe...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.99,0:13:20.55,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...at the edge of a cliff?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.19,0:13:23.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.48,0:13:26.81,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand a thing you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.81,0:13:28.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought up the anthropic principle...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.99,0:13:30.67,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...to draw a comparison.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.67,0:13:32.52,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't gotten to Suzumiya-san yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.85,0:13:33.91,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So tell me already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.91,0:13:36.01,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you, Nagato, and Asahina-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.01,0:13:37.28,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...all like Haruhi so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.96,0:13:40.86,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe her to be a charming person.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.86,0:13:42.46,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But let's set that aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.87,0:13:43.96,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.35,0:13:47.70,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I once said that the world may have been created...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.70,0:13:48.75,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...by Suzumiya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.99,0:13:50.29,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Annoys the hell out of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.29,0:13:51.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I guess I still remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.22,0:13:55.29,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She has the ability to realize wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.61,0:13:57.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make that kind of an assertion with a straight face.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.09,0:13:59.31,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzumiya-san is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:14:01.18,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...positive that aliens exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.18,0:14:03.42,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She wished it to be so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.42,0:14:04.94,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why Yuki Nagato is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.24,0:14:08.14,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Similarly, she wished for time travelers to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.14,0:14:10.59,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why Mikuru Asahina is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.90,0:14:12.22,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.22,0:14:14.12,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...am also here for the sole reason that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:16.32,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...Suzumiya-san wished it so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.32,0:14:17.92,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Like. I. Said.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.92,0:14:19.52,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.12,0:14:21.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It was three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.15,0:14:22.88,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Screw three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.88,0:14:23.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sick of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.39,0:14:25.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,One day I suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.60,0:14:27.47,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...became aware of certain powers within myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.47,0:14:29.62,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...as well as how to use those powers without knowing why.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.20,0:14:32.22,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Other people with the same powers...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.22,0:14:34.58,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...experienced similar awakenings.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.05,0:14:35.93,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.93,0:14:39.11,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...we also knew that Haruhi Suzumiya was the cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.11,0:14:40.70,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot explain why.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.70,0:14:42.88,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We just ended up with that knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.88,0:14:45.42,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just say I give you the benefit of doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.42,0:14:47.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I still don't see how Haruhi can do all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.86,0:14:50.30,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We found it hard to believe ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.30,0:14:52.69,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How could a single girl have transformed the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.69,0:14:53.44,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.44,0:14:56.35,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...perhaps even created the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.77,0:15:00.03,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And that girl finds this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.03,0:15:02.28,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...to be a boring place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.28,0:15:03.95,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a terrifying situation to behold.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.95,0:15:04.45,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.93,0:15:05.93,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.26,0:15:08.53,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If she's capable of creating this world at will...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.53,0:15:10.79,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...she could undo the world we know...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.79,0:15:13.08,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...and create her desired world from scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.43,0:15:15.06,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be quite literally...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.06,0:15:16.97,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...the end of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.97,0:15:17.90,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.90,0:15:20.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...we would have no way of knowing if it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.51,0:15:21.40,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.40,0:15:24.32,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The world we believe to be unique...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.32,0:15:27.63,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...may actually be the latest in a string of reincarnations.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.63,0:15:30.78,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then reveal your true identity to Haruhi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.78,0:15:32.77,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Once she knows that espers really exist...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.77,0:15:34.06,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...she'll be ecstatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.29,0:15:36.94,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She might stop thinking about changing the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.94,0:15:38.85,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That would pose another problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.85,0:15:39.95,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If Suzumiya-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.95,0:15:44.03,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...believes the existence of espers to be a common occurrence...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.27,0:15:46.87,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...the world would really end up that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.87,0:15:49.58,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The laws of physics would be bent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.58,0:15:51.61,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The entire universe would erupt into chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.95,0:15:54.17,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If Haruhi wished for you people to exist...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.17,0:15:56.69,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...why hasn't she noticed yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.69,0:15:57.64,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that odd?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.98,0:16:02.46,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Her desire for aliens, time travelers, and espers to exist...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.46,0:16:05.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...contradicts with her common sense...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.23,0:16:07.97,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...which says they cannot exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.97,0:16:10.75,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She is indeed eccentric in her speech and conduct...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.75,0:16:11.97,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...but she is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.97,0:16:15.75,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...a normal person with rational reasoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.41,0:16:20.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Her sandstorm-level of energy during middle school...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.23,0:16:22.47,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...has alleviated substantially the past few months.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.47,0:16:25.69,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I would have preferred that she continue to calm down...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.69,0:16:27.11,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...but once she came here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.11,0:16:28.94,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...a tornado touched down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.30,0:16:30.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.78,0:16:32.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It is your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.25,0:16:33.75,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What did I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.09,0:16:37.61,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You were the one who gave her the idea to form this questionable club.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.91,0:16:39.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Your conversation...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.51,0:16:43.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...gave her the inspiration to make a club made up of strange individuals.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.89,0:16:45.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The responsibility is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.04,0:16:47.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,As a result...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.25,0:16:51.04,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...low-ranked members from the three forces interested in Suzumiya-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.04,0:16:53.18,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...have gathered together in one group.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.91,0:16:55.07,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a false charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.32,0:16:58.26,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.26,0:17:00.65,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't the only reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.63,0:17:18.04,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It may be a bit late to say this after coming this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.04,0:17:20.27,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You can still back out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.27,0:17:21.61,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a bit late, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.64,0:17:25.41,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you close your eyes for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.41,0:17:26.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll only take a few seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.26,0:17:34.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.49,0:17:35.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're freaking me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.91,0:17:39.26,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.72,0:17:45.02,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The void within a dimensional fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.76,0:17:47.68,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A place separated from our world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.36,0:17:49.40,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Closed space.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.61,0:17:52.63,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The middle of this crosswalk happened to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.63,0:17:54.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...the "wall" of this closed space.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.91,0:17:57.10,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Its radius is approximately five kilometers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.10,0:17:59.79,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot gain entry through ordinary, physical measures.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.63,0:18:02.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,One of the powers I possess...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.51,0:18:04.82,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...is the ability to enter this space.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.35,0:18:08.59,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Picture a dome-shaped space rising from the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.59,0:18:09.97,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We would be on the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.85,0:18:12.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.25,0:18:15.18,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...everything's happening as normal on the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.67,0:18:18.33,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,An average person will be unable to stumble into this place...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.33,0:18:19.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...most of the time, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.90,0:18:23.91,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Closed space occurs completely arbitrarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.28,0:18:26.59,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There have been instances where they occurred every other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.59,0:18:29.16,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There were also times when months went by without incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.16,0:18:30.82,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Only one thing is certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.82,0:18:33.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This space is created whenever...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.49,0:18:35.55,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...Suzumiya-san becomes mentally unstable.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.01,0:18:38.96,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I am able to detect the emergence of closed space.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.96,0:18:40.58,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,As well as gain entry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.58,0:18:43.70,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, my powers are not limited to those.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.79,0:18:45.75,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You could say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.75,0:18:49.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...I've been granted powers which reflect Suzumiya-san's rationality.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.39,0:18:53.97,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If this world is like a pimple resulting from her unstable state...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.97,0:18:56.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...I would be the medicine that treats it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.23,0:18:58.35,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Your metaphors are hard to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.60,0:19:00.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,People often tell me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.15,0:19:02.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, you are quite impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.56,0:19:05.20,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a hint of surprise after witnessing this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.20,0:19:06.81,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already been through a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.54,0:19:08.95,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I see that it has begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.95,0:19:10.40,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Please look behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.06,0:19:23.85,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When Suzumiya-san's irritation passes a certain point...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.85,0:19:25.53,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...these giants appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.87,0:19:28.38,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They wreck their surroundings...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.38,0:19:30.30,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...to relieve her stress, I would assume.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.36,0:19:33.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't allow them to run loose in the real world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.99,0:19:35.76,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why closed space is created...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.76,0:19:38.22,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...and the destruction only transpires within.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.86,0:19:40.67,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Quite a rational method, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.02,0:19:45.04,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The laws of physics would dictate that its legs be unable to support its own weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.04,0:19:47.98,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It would appear that it is not bound by logic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.37,0:19:50.21,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mobilizing an army...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.21,0:19:52.58,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...wouldn't be enough to stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:54.73,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So you just let it rampage around!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.48,0:19:56.70,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Please watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.70,0:19:59.36,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,My colleagues.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.75,0:20:00.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Like myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.96,0:20:03.22,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...they were granted power by Suzumiya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.22,0:20:04.62,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Giant hunters.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.04,0:20:05.86,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.86,0:20:07.17,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I must join them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.85,0:20:20.64,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is just ridiculous, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.67,0:20:41.33,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.33,0:20:44.18,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There is one last sight for you to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.06,0:20:46.91,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What else could there possibly be?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.64,0:20:50.01,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Once the blue monster is defeated...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.01,0:20:51.88,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...closed space is destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.17,0:20:53.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite the spectacle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.31,0:21:08.73,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.96,0:21:09.80,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.18,0:21:11.74,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Those blue monsters...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.74,0:21:13.41,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We call them divine ones...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.41,0:21:15.12,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,"Celestials."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.12,0:21:18.65,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,"Celestials" are linked to Suzumiya-san's mental state.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.65,0:21:20.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,As are we.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.99,0:21:22.78,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Only when closed space is created...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.78,0:21:24.97,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...when "Celestials" are created...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.97,0:21:27.33,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...am I able to use abnormal powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.68,0:21:30.67,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And those powers can only be used within closed space.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.02,0:21:31.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,For instance...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.89,0:21:33.84,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...I currently have no power.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.64,0:21:37.64,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,As for why we are the only ones with such powers...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.05,0:21:39.91,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I would assume that any person would have sufficed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.91,0:21:41.82,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We just happened to be chosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.27,0:21:46.86,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot leave the actions of the "Celestials" unchecked.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.86,0:21:49.69,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,For the greater the extent of destruction the "Celestials" wreak...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.69,0:21:52.06,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...the more closed space will expand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.06,0:21:53.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The space you just saw...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.60,0:21:55.84,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...was one of the smaller ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.84,0:21:58.06,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If we leave it alone it will continue to expand...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.06,0:22:00.65,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...eventually covering the entire world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.42,0:22:02.81,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And in the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.81,0:22:04.64,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...that gray space...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.64,0:22:07.45,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...will take the place of our world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.45,0:22:09.00,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you know this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.69,0:22:12.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I just ended up with the knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.58,0:22:15.68,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The same goes for everyone in the "Agency."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.04,0:22:17.75,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If we did not act...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.75,0:22:19.96,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...the world would surely be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.93,0:22:22.43,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Quite a quandary.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.26,0:22:26.35,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take note of any trends in Suzumiya-san's behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.35,0:22:28.94,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Her mental state has been stable for a while now...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.94,0:22:31.07,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...but recently, there have been signs of activation.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.07,0:22:33.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's duties were the first in a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.49,0:22:35.03,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I do take note...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.03,0:22:36.72,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...what is that going to accomplish?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.03,0:22:37.70,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.70,0:22:39.39,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You never know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.39,0:22:44.22,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I would prefer to leave everything to you, myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.22,0:22:45.46,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There are those among us...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.46,0:22:48.20,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...with complicated intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.58,0:22:51.80,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Koizumi told me to note trends in Haruhi's behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.15,0:22:55.40,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nagato told me to be careful for some unknown reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.88,0:23:00.30,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Regardless, I didn't expect anything to happen soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.30,0:23:02.46,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I had the power of foresight...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.46,0:23:06.35,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and had known that an extraordinary ordeal would occur the very next day...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.95,0:23:09.58,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...I wouldn't have been so laid-back.
